---
layout: base.njk
title: Sponsor ACM CAIS 2026
description: Sponsorship opportunities for ACM CAIS 2026 — the inaugural ACM Conference on AI and Agentic Systems. Gold, Silver, and Bronze tiers plus à la carte options.
permalink: /pages/sponsors/
extraStyles: |
  .sponsor-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: url('/assets/images/hero ultralight gradient.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    padding: 4.5rem 0;
  }
  .sponsor-hero h1, .sponsor-hero p {
    color: var(--eerie-black);
  }
  .section-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .2px;
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
  }
  .anchor {
    scroll-margin-top: 84px;
  }

  /* Tier cards */
  .tier-card {
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    background: var(--seasalt);
    transition: border-color 200ms linear;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .tier-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--olive-moss);
  }
  .tier-gold {
    border: 2px solid var(--cais-accent);
    position: relative;
  }
  .tier-gold::before {
    content: "Premier";
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--cais-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
  .tier-silver {
    border: 2px solid var(--davys-gray);
  }
  .tier-bronze {
    border: 2px solid var(--platinum);
  }
  .tier-price {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .tier-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .tier-gold .tier-name { color: var(--cais-accent); }
  .tier-silver .tier-name { color: var(--davys-gray); }
  .tier-bronze .tier-name { color: #8b7355; }

  .tier-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }
  .tier-card ul li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--platinum);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .tier-card ul li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .tier-card ul li i {
    color: var(--cais-accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* À la carte tables */
  .alacarte-table th {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--davys-gray);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--platinum);
  }
  .alacarte-table td {
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .alacarte-table .price-cell {
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Sponsor tier display */
  .sponsor-tier { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .sponsor-tier-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--platinum);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .sponsor-tier-label.gold { color: var(--cais-accent); border-color: var(--cais-accent); }
  .sponsor-tier-label.silver { color: var(--davys-gray); border-color: var(--davys-gray); }
  .sponsor-tier-label.bronze { color: #8b7355; border-color: #8b7355; }
  .sponsor-tier-label.supporting { color: var(--davys-gray); border-color: var(--platinum); }
  .sponsor-logos {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .sponsor-logos a {
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 150ms ease;
  }
  .sponsor-logos a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
  .sponsor-logos.gold img { height: 60px; width: auto; }
  .sponsor-logos.silver img { height: 48px; width: auto; }
  .sponsor-logos.bronze img { height: 36px; width: auto; }
  .sponsor-logos.supporting img { height: 28px; width: auto; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sponsor-hero { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .tier-price { font-size: 1.35rem; }
    .sponsor-logos.gold img { height: 48px; }
    .sponsor-logos.silver img { height: 36px; }
  }
---

<header class="sponsor-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">Sponsor ACM CAIS 2026</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-3">ACM Conference on AI and Agentic Systems</p>
    <p class="mb-0"><strong>San Jose, CA • May 26–29, 2026</strong></p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row g-5">

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="col-lg-8">

        <!-- Intro -->
        <section class="mb-5">
          <p class="lead">ACM CAIS is the inaugural ACM conference on AI and agentic systems — a high-signal gathering of researchers and practitioners building the next generation of compound AI architectures.</p>
          <p>Your sponsorship puts your organization in front of the people defining this space — from leading academic labs to industry teams deploying compound AI systems at scale.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Sponsorship Tiers -->
        <section id="tiers" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-4">Sponsorship Tiers</h2>
          <div class="row g-4">

            <!-- Gold -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="tier-card tier-gold">
                <div class="tier-name">Gold Sponsor</div>
                <div class="tier-price">$20,000</div>
                <ul>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Premium tabletop in main foyer</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Pop-up banners + branded table</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>5 complimentary registrations</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Logo: website, program, signage, slides</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Opening ceremony acknowledgment</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Video recording acknowledgment</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Job postings shared with attendees</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Branded giveaways at booth</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Silver -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="tier-card tier-silver">
                <div class="tier-name">Silver Sponsor</div>
                <div class="tier-price">$12,000</div>
                <ul>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Standard tabletop in main foyer</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>2 complimentary registrations</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Logo: website, program, signage, slides</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Opening ceremony acknowledgment</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Job postings shared with attendees</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Branded giveaways at booth</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bronze -->
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="tier-card tier-bronze">
                <div class="tier-name">Bronze Sponsor</div>
                <div class="tier-price">$6,000</div>
                <ul>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>1 complimentary registration</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Logo: website + program</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Opening ceremony acknowledgment</li>
                  <li><i class="bi bi-check2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Branded giveaways (no booth)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- À La Carte -->
        <section id="alacarte" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-2">À La Carte Sponsorships</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">Available independently or as add-ons to any tier.</p>

          <h3 class="h6 fw-bold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Food &amp; Beverage</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive mb-4">
            <table class="table alacarte-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">Opportunity</th>
                  <th scope="col">Investment</th>
                  <th scope="col">Details</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>Lunch Sponsorship</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$25,000/day</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">x4 available</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Afternoon Break</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$12,000/day</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">x4 available</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Morning Coffee Break</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$10,000/day</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">x4 available</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Hydration Station</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$2,500</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Branded cups + signage</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <h3 class="h6 fw-bold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Ambient Brand Presence</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive mb-4">
            <table class="table alacarte-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">Opportunity</th>
                  <th scope="col">Investment</th>
                  <th scope="col">Details</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>WiFi Sponsorship</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$7,000</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Branded SSID + signage</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Lanyard Logo</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$5,000</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Per sponsor, max 4</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Hotel Key Cards</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$5,000</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Branded room keys, 400</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Charging Station</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$4,000</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Branded hightop tables</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <h3 class="h6 fw-bold text-uppercase text-muted mb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Event Collateral &amp; Space</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table alacarte-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">Opportunity</th>
                  <th scope="col">Investment</th>
                  <th scope="col">Details</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>Photo Wall / Backdrop</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$3,000</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Step-and-repeat in foyer</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>Bag Insert</td>
                  <td class="price-cell">$1,500</td>
                  <td class="small text-muted">Sponsor ships item</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Partnership with AI Engineer World's Fair -->
        <section id="aie-partnership" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Partnership with AI Engineer World's Fair</h2>
          <div class="highlight-box p-4">
            <p class="mb-0">CAIS 2026 is partnered with the <a href="https://www.ai.engineer/worldsfair" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AI Engineer World's Fair</a> (June 29–July 2, Moscone West, SF, 6,000+ attendees). Top accepted papers cross over to present at both events, extending CAIS's reach into the practitioner engineering community. Sponsors benefit from visibility across both venues and audiences.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Sponsor -->
        <section id="why-sponsor" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Why Sponsor ACM CAIS?</h2>
          <div class="highlight-box p-4">
            <p class="mb-3">ACM CAIS is the first ACM venue dedicated to compound AI and agentic systems — architectures combining multiple models, tools, and verification methods into reliable, deployable systems. The steering committee includes researchers from MIT, Stanford, UC Berkeley, Google DeepMind, and Microsoft Research who defined this paradigm.</p>
            <p class="mb-0">Sponsoring the inaugural conference positions your organization at the ground floor of a research community that will shape how AI systems are built and deployed for years to come.</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Get in Touch -->
        <section id="contact" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>Ready to sponsor, or have questions about custom packages?</p>
          <div class="highlight-box p-3 mb-4" style="max-width: 24rem;">
            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Josh Quicksall</h3>
            <p class="small text-muted mb-2">Sponsorship Chair</p>
            <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.sponsorship }}">{{ site.contact.sponsorship }}</a>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.sponsorship }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4" style="background:var(--cais-accent); border:none; color:#fff;">
            <i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Us About Sponsorship
          </a>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Sponsors -->
        <section id="current-sponsors" class="anchor mb-5">
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Our Sponsors</h2>

          {% if sponsors.gold.length %}
          <div class="sponsor-tier">
            <div class="sponsor-tier-label gold">Gold</div>
            <div class="sponsor-logos gold">
              {% for s in sponsors.gold %}
              {% if s.logo %}
              <a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src="/assets/images/{{ s.logo }}" alt="{{ s.name }}" loading="lazy" />
              </a>
              {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if sponsors.silver.length %}
          <div class="sponsor-tier">
            <div class="sponsor-tier-label silver">Silver</div>
            <div class="sponsor-logos silver">
              {% for s in sponsors.silver %}
              <a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src="/assets/images/{{ s.logo }}" alt="{{ s.name }}" loading="lazy" />
              </a>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if sponsors.bronze.length %}
          <div class="sponsor-tier">
            <div class="sponsor-tier-label bronze">Bronze</div>
            <div class="sponsor-logos bronze">
              {% for s in sponsors.bronze %}
              <a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src="/assets/images/{{ s.logo }}" alt="{{ s.name }}" loading="lazy" />
              </a>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if sponsors.supporting.length %}
          <div class="sponsor-tier">
            <div class="sponsor-tier-label supporting">Supporting Sponsors</div>
            <div class="sponsor-logos supporting">
              {% for s in sponsors.supporting %}
              <a href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src="/assets/images/{{ s.logo }}" alt="{{ s.name }}" loading="lazy" />
              </a>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if not sponsors.gold.length and not sponsors.silver.length and not sponsors.bronze.length and not sponsors.supporting.length %}
          <div class="highlight-box p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-muted mb-0"><i class="bi bi-stars me-2"></i>Sponsor logos will appear here as partnerships are confirmed.</p>
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </section>

      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <aside>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="d-grid mb-4">
            <a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.sponsorship }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg py-3 fw-bold" style="background:var(--cais-accent); border:none; color:#fff; font-size:1.1rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- At a Glance -->
          <div class="card mb-4" style="border: 2px solid var(--cais-accent); border-radius: 4px;">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>At a Glance</h3>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="small text-muted">Expected attendance</div>
                <div class="fw-bold">500+ researchers, engineers, and industry leaders</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="small text-muted">Who attends</div>
                <div class="small">Faculty, PhD students, research engineers, and technical leaders from top universities and companies building agentic AI systems</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="small text-muted">Location</div>
                <div class="fw-bold">San Jose, CA</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="small text-muted">Dates</div>
                <div class="fw-bold">May 26–29, 2026</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-2"></i>On This Page</h3>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#tiers">Sponsorship Tiers</a></li>
                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#alacarte">À La Carte Options</a></li>
                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#why-sponsor">Why Sponsor?</a></li>
                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#contact">Get in Touch</a></li>
                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#current-sponsors">Current Sponsors</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tier Summary -->
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bookmark me-2"></i>Tier Summary</h3>
              <table class="table table-sm mb-0">
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="small fw-bold" style="color: var(--cais-accent);">Gold</td>
                    <td class="text-end small fw-bold">$20,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="small fw-bold" style="color: var(--davys-gray);">Silver</td>
                    <td class="text-end small fw-bold">$12,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="small fw-bold" style="color: #8b7355;">Bronze</td>
                    <td class="text-end small fw-bold">$6,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-top">
                    <td class="small text-muted">À la carte</td>
                    <td class="text-end small text-muted">from $1,500</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

        </aside>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
